Comment: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:00.16,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:120160,120160}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:06.41,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:120954,126418}Maya, despite Onodera's terrible plot,\Nstood on the stage all by herself…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:09.00,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:126418,129004}…and received strong support from\Nthe audience at the National Acting Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:12.46,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:129004,132466}However, they lost the competition due to Onodera's interruption…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.59,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132466,135594}…and Tsukikage Theater was forced to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:20.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:135594,140140}The only members left with Tsukikage Theater are Maya and four others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.14,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141141,147147}{\an5\pos(766,720)\fscy95\blur1\fad(1200,0)}—Episode 08—\NMasumi's Passion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.48,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:147981,149483}Tsukikage Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153737,155822}Teacher, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155822,159951}I'll get a part time job and try\Nnot to be a burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159951,162245}I'll practice even harder from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162245,164247}Teacher, we'll do the same, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164247,166416}Tsukikage Theater is not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166416,169628}It's just that we just have to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169628,172547}We'll just have to start right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172547,176468}Yes. We can't let Ondine destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176468,178679}Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183225,185602}Maya. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186061,189356}Please take care of yourself, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189356,191149}You do the same, Genzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192109,194653}Please don't worry about your expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194653,199700}I'll work hard and take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199700,202744}So please don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202744,203704}Genzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219344,221179}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221179,222931}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225434,227185}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228353,230981}We haven't had any new big talents lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230981,234359}That's right. Well, I don't know about big,\Nbut I saw an interesting girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234359,235444}Where at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235444,236945}At the National Acting Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236945,239614}She attracted the audience's attention all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239614,241158}Kitajima Maya was her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241158,242200}Hmm. What is she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242200,244828}Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244828,247497}But I heard Toride-san has an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247497,249458}Toride as in that well-known scout?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249458,251209}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251209,252669}Okay, we should check her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263430,264890}My name is Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264890,268059}I have worked for the CEO till now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268059,270479}…but he assigned me to you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270479,271688}Yes, I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273356,277778}Could you call Mr. Onodera from Ondine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277778,279738}I would like to speak to him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279738,281156}I'm on it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285994,289164}Hello. This is Mizuki from Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289164,289998}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289998,291416}May I speak to Mr. Onodera, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292918,296546}I'll have her for Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299257,301635}Where are we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301635,303887}A small, one bedroom apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303887,306973}Sayaka, Mina and Taiko will stay on the second floor of a nearby bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306973,309184}Rei, you're from Tōkyō, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309184,310685}Why don't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310685,312479}Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312479,314856}Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314856,317108}I like acting, and I like you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317108,319945}That's why I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347722,351184}Here, this will be our castle from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351184,354312}Yeah, forget about tomorrow,\Nand let's get off to a new start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354312,355355}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355355,359901}Yesterday won't come back even if you think about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359901,363113}So let's think about tomorrow and how are we going to live tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363655,364614}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364614,370579}And if things are not good tomorrow, there's always the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371830,372914}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374624,377586}{\i1}That's right, and I will be an actress someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379796,380755}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380755,383008}Be quiet! You're about to wreck the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383008,384718}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390891,393226}{\i1}Even though Tsukikage Theater has gone out of business…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393226,394477}{\i1}…she…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394477,396771}{\i1}…she won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402319,405405}{\i1}When and how will she come in my way again?{NOTE:あなたはいつ どんな形でまた現れるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405405,407157}{\i1}I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409326,410827}Rei, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412621,413872}I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418043,420045}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420045,422339}Good morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422339,424758}Time for voice training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425759,426885}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426885,428219}Okay, we'll be right there, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436686,440190}Ta·chi·tsu·te·to, na·ni·nu·ne·no…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440190,444945}Na·n·do ni nu·me·tte, na·ni ne·ba·ru…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452494,453912}Sakurakōji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459084,462170}I thought I would catch you if I waited at your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462170,465882}You moved without letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465882,466967}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480063,481231}Masumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482607,485235}Everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485235,485860}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486903,487862}Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487862,488738}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502877,506965}You'll play the knight's role at the student play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506965,508341}How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508341,509592}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509592,512220}You seem happier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512220,514014}That's my only talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514014,516349}I can't be depressed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516349,519227}So I'll try to think about tomorrow instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519227,520979}Tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520979,525233}Yes, I want to act as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525233,527235}What about school?\NYou'll be in high school next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527235,530530}Yeah. But I want to act,\Nand I have to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530530,532532}Besides, my grades are terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535744,537370}Oh, is this your script?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539497,541332}Wow, how interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541332,544210}You'll be a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544210,545295}How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547756,548757}"Yuria."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548757,551468}"I don't have fame,\Nstatus, or money."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551468,554512}"Yuria, I don't have fame, status, or money."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554512,558099}"But I have plenty of love you in my heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558099,559768}"Don't say anymore, Floria."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559768,565732}"If my father finds out that we're meeting like this… he'll be furious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565732,567192}"Don't go, Yuria!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567192,570278}"My heart is with you from the first time I saw you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570278,573364}"Please tell me, Yuria, that you love me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573364,574741}"They way you smile…"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574741,575992}"The way you move…"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575992,579788}"I think of you every night."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579788,581664}"To be by your side."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581664,582957}"To look at you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582957,584375}"To love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584375,587212}"And to help you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587212,590173}"That's my only wish!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593176,594928}Oh, keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603812,605313}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605313,607190}Let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610527,614322}{\i1}He's all quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614322,615740}{\i1}How weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632340,633341}Hey, Masumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638221,641266}Did you think about what we talked about the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641266,647021}Yeah, but you know that Kitajima Maya hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649232,651526}Even if we were to give her an excellent offer…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651526,655697}…I don't think she'll fall for Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655697,659075}Besides, all the scouts will be all over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659075,660869}They've forgotten about her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660869,664038}They are all busy promoting a British rock band.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666666,668918}You're such a powerful man.
Comment: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:14.67,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:674674,674674}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:18.46,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:678469,678469}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:21.47,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:681472,681472}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689772,691065}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691065,693318}Oh, Sakurakōji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693318,695111}I heard you wanted to talk to me about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695111,696988}Oh, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696988,698865}I want to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703453,708458}Well, the girl you have been seeing from Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708458,711836}You mean, Kitajima… Maya-san…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714339,717300}What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732440,734859}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738321,740323}Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740323,741908}Three coffees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742867,744786}I'd like some pizza toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744786,745662}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745662,747163}For me, too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747163,748998}Okay, I'll bring it right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750917,752085}She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755380,760093}We asked for a waitress, not a waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760093,761552}You're still talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761552,762762}Oh, Maya, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762762,764681}Rei, this place is hopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764681,769686}Of course. I'm the only one who graduated from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769686,771437}Leave it all up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771437,773982}You were going to go to college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773982,775858}My parents were going to make me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775858,778778}Excuse me? Can you take our order?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778778,780238}Yes, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781322,784200}Not you, mister, but her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784200,785451}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790999,793459}I have to look for a job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805930,807390}Part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807390,809809}Oh, no. We have enough people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809809,811894}Besides, aren't you still in junior high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811894,813062}But, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813062,814605}No, just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816232,817942}{\i1}It's harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817942,820236}{\i1}I still haven't even paid my tuition yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.28,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:820862,822280}Maya was becoming irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.69,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:822280,824699}Not being able to practice was the hardest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.53,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:824699,826534}When they started practicing at their apartment…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.61,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:826534,828619}…all they got was complaints from their neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.29,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:828619,832290}They wandered parks at night in search of a place they could practice in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:55.25,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:832290,835251}She had school in the daytime and kept on looking for jobs after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.25,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:835251,838254}Her life was getting harder and harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838254,840882}I haven't practiced for two weeks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842133,843134}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843134,845887}Your shoulders are crying, Maya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845887,847221}Sakurakōji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856773,857982}To Ondine Theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857982,860068}Yeah, it's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860068,864989}Mr. Onodera would like to have you as a scholarship student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864989,866491}Mr. Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868826,873956}I would like to comment on the play by Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873956,878461}Not only that she didn't play it by the book,\Nbut she continued her selfish play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878461,883049}Tsukikage Theater and Ondine had to be enemies at the National Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883049,887720}But Mr. Onodera says he hates to see your talent get buried without a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888679,891599}Sakurakōji-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891599,896354}Maya-chan, with Ondine you can study acting without any worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:00.10,Default,,1,1,0,,{TIME:896354,900108}Tuition is all free, of course, and you can stay in the dorms of Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.56,Default,,1,1,0,,{TIME:900108,902568}They pay for school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904862,905988}Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905988,908616}Let's study acting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908616,912912}Remember we once said we wanted to get on stage together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912912,914997}Sakurakōji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914997,916999}So, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918960,920586}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920586,922088}Maya-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928553,933516}I can't betray Miss Tsukikage and my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933516,934600}I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934600,936144}This is for your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936144,938229}You have to put yourself\Nas your first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938229,940064}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940064,942900}I love my crew at Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942900,944694}More than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953911,956330}I'm sorry. I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961085,962336}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962336,965590}I was inconsiderate. I didn't even think about your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969302,970887}I'll go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970887,973139}But I won't give up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973139,974307}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980855,982398}Sakurakōji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985151,987236}{\i1}To be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987236,989530}{\i1}To look at you. To love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989530,994035}{\i1}And to help you. That's my only wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002668,1003920}See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003920,1005254}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005254,1007006}Working hard on Sunday, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007006,1008674}Sunday is the busiest day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008674,1010635}Why don't you go out yourself today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011719,1013804}Hey! Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013804,1015139}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020394,1021771}{\i1}It's been three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021771,1023606}{\i1}Everyone is busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025399,1026484}{\i1}I want to act!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:19.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1034659,1039497}King Lear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045086,1046128}Wow, a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046128,1048548}I really would like to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055054,1055888}Ayumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063145,1065439}Oh, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066566,1068150}You're from Ondine…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068150,1070444}You need to hurry up. The play is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071279,1073573}No, I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073573,1076117}At least enjoy the pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088879,1090756}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090756,1092341}Hello, Masumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092341,1095678}Long time no see, Mrs. Himekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095678,1096929}Hi, Mizuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096929,1103144}I'm surprised to hear that you, the CEO's secretary, are working for Masumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103144,1107356}Masumi-sama will soon take over Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107356,1112028}I wanted to be of any help so I accepted that proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112028,1115281}Then, you will be the voice of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119702,1121662}Here, the show is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121662,1122663}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126542,1129086}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129086,1134759}She just stands there looking at the pictures from the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134759,1136636}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136636,1137678}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143476,1144602}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147730,1152068}I'm so silly. I know I can't go in, but I can't leave either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154487,1156280}Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156280,1158366}I'm running an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158366,1160409}Here, someone told me to give these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162953,1164705}Oh, that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164705,1166749}Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167291,1167875}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170002,1171879}Hey, wait. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172922,1175591}I don't know. He left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175591,1177927}Wait! What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177927,1179261}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187311,1189063}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189063,1191482}Thank you, Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192733,1195027}She's gotten the reserved seat!\NI'm envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201534,1203744}Do what you want, Cordelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203744,1206038}Take your words with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206038,1209583}From this point on, we are not\Nfather and son anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209583,1212211}You're not my blood anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233065,1234400}{\i1}It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234400,1236694}{\i1}I wonder if I can act like that someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245911,1247705}You were here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247705,1250750}Is it okay for a junior high student to stay out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250750,1251709}It's nine o'clock already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251709,1252710}Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252710,1253878}I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253878,1255171}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255171,1256672}Can I give you a ride, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258090,1260384}By they way, I heard you rejected the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262470,1266015}If you join Ondine, you can study acting without worrying about making a living…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266015,1269059}…and fully focus on studying acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269059,1271812}You were the one!\NIt was your plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273564,1278068}You want to get me away from Miss Tsukikage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278068,1280279}What would you do if that's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280279,1281739}No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290831,1293000}She broke your heart beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294126,1296462}{\i1}She must hate me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297087,1298172}Masumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298172,1300424}You seem to have so much interest in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305137,1306764}It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306764,1308349}I can't let a golden egg pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319944,1321320}Is that really the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334583,1337628}I wonder who in the world he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337628,1339922}Thank you, Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349515,1352351}Maya's life has been hard without being able to practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352351,1356438}…but Maya was building even more passion for acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356438,1360109}All for Mr. Purple Rose,\Nwho's always looking out for her.
